<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CodingKita | Jasa Pembuatan Website UMKM Profesional & Terjangkau</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
    body { font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; }
    .glass { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); }
    
    /* Utility untuk Gradasi Teks yang Kompatibel */
    .gradient-text {
        background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, #2563eb, #7c3aed);
        
        background-clip: text;
        color: transparent;

        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        
        display: inline-block;
    }
</style>
</head>
<body class="bg-[#fcfcfd] text-slate-900">

    <nav class="glass sticky top-0 z-[100] border-b border-slate-100 py-4 px-6 md:px-20 flex justify-between items-center">
        <div class="text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter flex items-center gap-2">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white text-sm">
                <i class="fas fa-code"></i>
            </div>
            <span>Coding<span class="text-blue-600">Kita</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden md:flex space-x-8 font-semibold text-sm tracking-wide">
            <a href="#home" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">Beranda</a>
            <a href="#keunggulan" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">Keunggulan</a>
            <a href="#harga" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">Paket Harga</a>
            <a href="#faq" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">Tanya Jawab</a>
        </div>
        <a href="https://wa.me/628xxxx" class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-2.5 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-blue-700 transition shadow-lg shadow-blue-100 text-sm">
            Konsultasi Gratis
        </a>
    </nav>

    <header id="home" class="relative pt-20 pb-24 md:pt-32 md:pb-40 px-6 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="container mx-auto text-center relative z-10">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-[13px] font-bold mb-8 border border-blue-100">
                <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
                    <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-blue-400 opacity-75"></span>
                    <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-blue-500"></span>
                </span>
                Solusi Digital UMKM Masa Kini
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-[800] leading-[1.1] mb-8 tracking-tight text-slate-900">
                Wujudkan Website Impian <br> Bersama <span class="gradient-text text-blue-600">CodingKita.</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                Jasa pembuatan website profesional, fitur lengkap, dan SEO Friendly. Bantu bisnis UMKM-mu tampil lebih berkelas dan terpercaya.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-5">
                <a href="#harga" class="bg-slate-900 text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-2xl font-bold text-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-1">
                    Mulai Sekarang
                </a>
                <a href="https://wa.me/628xxxx" class="bg-white border border-slate-200 px-10 py-4 rounded-2xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-slate-50 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                    <i class="fab fa-whatsapp text-green-500"></i> Tanya Dulu
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -top-24 -left-24 w-96 h-96 bg-blue-100 rounded-full blur-[120px] opacity-50"></div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-24 -right-24 w-96 h-96 bg-indigo-100 rounded-full blur-[120px] opacity-50"></div>
    </header>

    <section id="keunggulan" class="py-24 bg-white px-6">
        <div class="container mx-auto">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between mb-16 gap-4">
                <div class="max-w-xl">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-4">Kenapa Harus CodingKita?</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 font-medium leading-relaxed">Kami mengutamakan kualitas koding dan kepuasan klien agar website Anda benar-benar menghasilkan uang.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-blue-600 font-bold hidden md:block">Slide untuk lihat keunggulan &rarr;</div>
            </div>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 hover:bg-white hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl mb-6 shadow-lg shadow-blue-200">
                        <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Peforma Kencang</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Website ringan dan cepat diakses, meminimalkan risiko calon pembeli kabur karena web lemot.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 hover:bg-white hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-indigo-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl mb-6 shadow-lg shadow-indigo-200">
                        <i class="fas fa-lock"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Keamanan Terjamin</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Sudah termasuk SSL (HTTPS) gratis untuk melindungi data bisnis dan pelanggan Anda.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 hover:bg-white hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-purple-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl mb-6 shadow-lg shadow-purple-200">
                        <i class="fas fa-headset"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Support Responsif</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Ada masalah? Tim CodingKita siap membantu via WhatsApp kapanpun Anda butuhkan.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="harga" class="py-24 bg-slate-50 px-6">
        <div class="container mx-auto">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-4">Investasi Bisnis Terbaik</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-500 font-medium">Mulai kembangkan sayap bisnis digitalmu dengan budget hemat.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                <% packages.forEach(pkg => { %>
                <div class="bg-white p-8 md:p-12 rounded-[40px] border border-slate-200 flex flex-col h-full shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl transition duration-500">
                    <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-2"><%= pkg.name %></span>
                    <div class="text-5xl font-extrabold mb-8">Rp <%= pkg.price %></div>
                    <ul class="space-y-5 mb-12 flex-grow">
                        <% pkg.features.forEach(feature => { %>
                        <li class="flex items-start text-slate-700 font-semibold">
                            <i class="fas fa-check text-green-500 mt-1 mr-4 bg-green-50 p-1 rounded-full text-[10px]"></i>
                            <%= feature %>
                        </li>
                        <% }) %>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="https://wa.me/628xxxx?text=Halo+CodingKita,+mau+tanya+<%= pkg.name %>" class="w-full py-4 rounded-2xl text-center font-bold bg-blue-600 text-white hover:bg-slate-900 transition-all duration-300">
                        Ambil Promo Ini
                    </a>
                </div>
                <% }) %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="faq" class="py-24 bg-white px-6">
        <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-16">Paling Sering Ditanyakan</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <details class="group p-6 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 bg-slate-50 cursor-pointer transition-all">
                    <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold text-lg list-none">
                        <span>Berapa lama proses pembuatan?</span>
                        <span class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down text-blue-600"></i></span>
                    </summary>
                    <div class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                        Estimasi pengerjaan adalah 2-5 hari kerja setelah data (logo, teks, gambar) kami terima dengan lengkap.
                    </div>
                </details>
                <details class="group p-6 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 bg-slate-50 cursor-pointer transition-all">
                    <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold text-lg list-none">
                        <span>Apakah ada biaya bulanan?</span>
                        <span class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down text-blue-600"></i></span>
                    </summary>
                    <div class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                        Tidak ada biaya bulanan. Pembayaran dilakukan per tahun untuk perpanjangan Domain & Hosting (sangat terjangkau!).
                    </div>
                </details>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-400 py-20 px-6">
        <div class="container mx-auto">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-16">
                <div class="col-span-2">
                    <div class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6">Coding<span class="text-blue-500">Kita</span></div>
                    <p class="max-w-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">Partner digital terpercaya untuk membantu UMKM tumbuh lebih besar melalui teknologi website yang cerdas dan efisien.</p>
                    <div class="flex gap-4">
                        <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 bg-slate-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white hover:bg-blue-600 transition"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
                        <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 bg-slate-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white hover:bg-blue-600 transition"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-6 italic underline decoration-blue-500">Menu</h4>
                    <ul class="space-y-4 font-medium">
                        <li><a href="#home" class="hover:text-white transition">Beranda</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#keunggulan" class="hover:text-white transition">Keunggulan</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#harga" class="hover:text-white transition">Paket Harga</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-6 italic underline decoration-blue-500">Kontak</h4>
                    <p class="mb-4 font-medium">📍 Grand Verona Regency, Gresik</p>
                    <p class="mb-4 font-medium">📧 p.rafidtito2@gmail.com</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="pt-8 border-t border-slate-800 text-center text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest">
                MADE WITH ❤️ BY <span class="text-white">CODINGKITA</span> &copy; 2026.
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>